      "title": "Solo Leveling",
      "author": "Chu gong",
      "summary": "The story is set in a world where mysterious \"Gates\" have appeared, connecting our world to dungeons filled with monsters. Humans who gained supernatural abilities to fight these monsters are known as Hunters. Unlike most RPG-style worlds, a Hunter’s rank—from E-rank (the weakest) to S-rank (the strongest)—is determined at the moment they awaken. It is impossible for a Hunter to get stronger through training or experience... except for one."
