      "title": "Second Life Ranker",
      "author": "Nong Nong, Sa Doyeon",
      "summary": "Second Life Ranker’ is a fantasy action series that tells the story of a young man who ventures into a perilous tower to uncover the truth behind his brother’s death. After finding his brother’s diary, he discovers a secret world filled with trials, monsters and powerful ‘Rankers’. Determined to avenge his brother and become stronger, he uses the knowledge contained in the diary to climb the tower at a pace that exceeds all expectations."
    },
